            <h1>
              如何提高中职计算机基础知识教学改革探讨
            </h1>
            <h2>
              How to improve Vocational Computer Basics Teaching Reform
            </h2>
            <div id="ctl00_LeftContentPlaceHolder_periodical">
              <p id="fulltext" style="visibility:visible">
                <a href="/Service/File/view/如何提高中职计算机基础知识教学改革探讨.aspx?ID=Periodical_jsjgprjyyy201101137" class="seeft">
                </a>
                <a href="/Service/File/download/Periodical_jsjgprjyyy201101137.aspx" class="downloadft">
                </a>
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
